description: In Thailand, the saying “Sabai Sabai” is a commonly used phase denoting a happy, peaceful, relaxed and carefree way of life… The Thai way of life. And, similar to the phrase Hakuna Matata, it means no worries, enjoy life to its fullest.So relax and enjoy a little Thai food from Sabai Sabai Mobile Thai featuring classic & flavorful Thai food made by people who’s mothers taught them the Thai way to cook, with love.
name: Sabai Sabai
